## üé® Design System Standards

### Neumorphic Design Principles
- **Accessibility First**: High contrast text, keyboard navigation, screen reader support
- **Functional Beauty**: Aesthetics support functionality, not override it
- **Consistent Interactions**: Predictable hover/focus/active states
- **Professional Appearance**: Suitable for educational/business environment

### Color Palette (STRICT)

**Note**: Using Tailwind CSS v4 with `@theme` blocks in `projojo_frontend/src/index.css`

```css
/* Tailwind v4 @theme block syntax */
@theme {
    --color-primary: #FF7F50;        /* Coral Primary */
    --color-dark-primary: #FF6347;   /* Darker variant (Tomato) */
    --color-light-primary: #FFA07A;  /* Lighter accent (Light Salmon) */
    
    /* Neumorphic Colors */
    --color-neu-bg: #EFEEEE;
    --color-neu-light: #FFFFFF;
    --color-neu-dark: #D1D9E6;
    
    /* Text Colors */
    --color-text-primary: #2D3748;
    --color-text-secondary: #4A5568;
    --color-text-muted: #718096;
}

:root {
    --primary: #FF7F50;              /* Coral - warm and inviting */
    
    /* Semantic Colors */
    --success: #22bb33;
    --warning: #ffa502;
    --error: #ff4757;
    --info: #4c79ff;
}
```

### Component Standards

#### Neumorphic Cards
```css
.neu-flat {
  background: #EFEEEE;
  box-shadow: 6px 6px 12px #D1D9E6, -6px -6px 12px #FFFFFF;
  border-radius: 1.5rem;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
}

.neu-pressed {
  background: #EFEEEE;
  box-shadow: inset 4px 4px 8px #D1D9E6, inset -4px -4px 8px #FFFFFF;
  border-radius: 1rem;
}

.neu-card-lg {
  background: #EFEEEE;
  box-shadow: 6px 6px 12px #D1D9E6, -6px -6px 12px #FFFFFF;
  border-radius: 2rem;
  padding: 2rem;
  border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
}
```

#### Buttons
- Use `.neu-btn` for secondary actions
- Use `.neu-btn-primary` for primary actions
- Legacy `.btn-primary` still available for compatibility
- Inset shadow for active states
- Focus rings for accessibility (Indigo with 30% opacity)
- Smooth transitions (0.2s ease)

#### Activity Indicators (V5 Standard)
- Subtle pulse animations (2s cycle)
- Green activity dots with soft glow
- Border-left accents for active states
- "Working" badges with consistent styling
- Priority color coding: High(red), Medium(orange), Low(green)

